This has to be a joke.

38:17.330 --> 38:21.584
I'm not fighting that skinny bitch.
I'll kill her.

38:21.667 --> 38:26.505
Yeah? Then you forfeit the match,
and your money.

38:26.589 --> 38:28.883
- Bullshit.
- [chuckles]

38:28.966 --> 38:35.681
Actually, this is a very cheap price
to save yourself much humiliation.

38:35.765 --> 38:37.558
What?

38:38.642 --> 38:42.063
Smart money is on the skinny bitch.

38:42.146 --> 38:43.731
[bell dings]

38:43.814 --> 38:46.901
- [referee shouts]
- [crowd cheers]

39:05.044 --> 39:07.588
We need to keep going to the city.

39:14.137 --> 39:15.305
No.

39:16.973 --> 39:18.141
What are you doing?

39:18.933 --> 39:20.393
I'm going to get the medicine back.

39:20.477 --> 39:23.354
- Don't talk crazy, Capheus.
- Anyone who doesn't want to come with me

39:23.438 --> 39:25.689
