- Capheus, please.

39:25.773 --> 39:28.318
- I don't expect you to come with me.
- We're partners.

39:28.401 --> 39:30.820
You have Elena. You have the kids.

39:30.903 --> 39:31.946
- I'm coming with you.
- No.

39:32.029 --> 39:33.697
- Start the car. I'm coming with you.
- No.

39:33.781 --> 39:35.992
[speaks foreign language]

39:36.534 --> 39:37.535
No.

39:38.911 --> 39:40.497
I'd follow you anywhere.

39:41.372 --> 39:44.334
I know. It's OK.

39:51.424 --> 39:55.761
My husband gave me that ring
43 years ago.

39:55.845 --> 39:58.556
It's all I have left of him.

40:00.891 --> 40:02.477
Let's go get it.

40:10.360 --> 40:12.153
May Jean-Claude protect you.

40:19.494 --> 40:21.662
- [referee] Yeah!
- [crowd cheering]

40:25.958 --> 40:27.668
[referee] Fighters...

40:30.129 --> 40:32.465
