- [crowd cheering]

40:37.094 --> 40:39.389
[shouts indistinctly]

41:15.049 --> 41:16.675
Aah! Fuck!

41:25.602 --> 41:27.353
Go, go, go, go, go!

41:39.740 --> 41:41.742
[crowd cheering]

41:42.701 --> 41:44.328
[man] Yah!

41:55.673 --> 41:56.966
[screams]

42:04.307 --> 42:05.182
