42:10.605 --> 42:12.440
[grunts]

42:55.650 --> 42:57.694
- [yells]
- [grunts]

43:00.904 --> 43:02.615
[yells]

43:09.288 --> 43:11.332
[yells]

43:21.091 --> 43:22.259
[shouts]

43:34.021 --> 43:35.356
[whispers] Help me.

43:38.234 --> 43:41.738
Help me, please.

43:46.950 --> 43:48.745
- [grunts]
- [crowd cheering]

43:58.254 --> 44:01.257
I'll kill you fucking slow.

44:04.468 --> 44:06.095
