44:16.897 --> 44:18.315
- [man yells]
- [shouts]

44:19.609 --> 44:20.818
Fuck!

44:23.571 --> 44:25.281
Aah!

44:31.370 --> 44:32.830
Aah!

44:35.124 --> 44:36.542
